# wisclabmisc

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of wisclabmisc is to reuse analysis functions across projects.

## Installation

You can install the development version of wisclabmisc from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("tjmahr/wisclabmisc")
```
